&lt;p&gt;Most of the Chinese translations of come from this site &lt;a href="http://pe-cn.github.io/"&gt;Project Euler | 欧拉计划&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hope you enjoy solving problems in Project Euler.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Project Euler exists to encourage, challenge, and develop the skills and enjoyment of anyone with an interest in the fascinating world of mathematics.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
